3049static void
3050cmplx_to_mem(int real, int imag, DTYPE dtype, int *addr, int *nme)
3051{
3052 int load;
3053 ILI_OP store;
3054 int size, msz;
3055 int r_op1, i_op1, i_op2;
3056 SPTR tmp;
3057
3058 assert(DT_ISCMPLX(dtype), "cmplx_to_mem: not complex dtype", dtype,
3059 ERR_Severe);
3060 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_CMPLX) {
3061 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000) && !imag) {
3062 load = IL_LDSCMPLX;
3063 store = IL_STSCMPLX;
3064 msz = MSZ_F8;
3065 } else {
3066 load = IL_LDSP;
3067 store = IL_STSP;
3068 msz = MSZ_F4;
3069 }
3070 } else {
3071 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000) && !imag) {
3072 load = IL_LDDCMPLX;
3073 store = IL_STDCMPLX;
3074 msz = MSZ_F16;
3075 } else {
3076 load = IL_LDDP;
3077 store = IL_STDP;
3078 msz = MSZ_F8;
3079 }
3080 }
3081 if (!XBIT(70, 0x40000000)) {
3082 size = size_of(dtype) / 2;
3083 } else {
3084 if (!imag)
3085 size = size_of(dtype);
3086 else
3087 size = size_of(dtype) / 2;
3088 if (ILI_OPC(real) == load) {
3089 r_op1 = ILI_OPND(real, 1);
3090 if (ILI_OPC(r_op1) == IL_ACON) {
3091 *addr = ILI_OPND(real, 1);
3092 *nme = ILI_OPND(real, 2);
3093 return;
3094 }
3095 }
3096 }
3097
3098 if (ILI_OPC(real) == load && ILI_OPC(imag) == load) {
3099 /* Direct load? */
3100 r_op1 = ILI_OPND(real, 1);
3101 i_op1 = ILI_OPND(imag, 1);
3102 if (ILI_OPC(r_op1) == IL_ACON && ILI_OPC(i_op1) == IL_ACON) {
3103 r_op1 = ILI_OPND(r_op1, 1);
3104 i_op1 = ILI_OPND(i_op1, 1);
3105 if (CONVAL1G(r_op1) == CONVAL1G(i_op1) &&
3106 ACONOFFG(r_op1) + size == ACONOFFG(i_op1)) {
3107 *addr = ILI_OPND(real, 1);
3108 *nme = NME_NM(ILI_OPND(real, 2));
3109 return;
3110 }
3111 }
3112
3113 /* Indirect load? */
3114 r_op1 = ILI_OPND(real, 1);
3115 i_op1 = ILI_OPND(imag, 1);
3116 if (ILI_OPC(i_op1) == IL_AADD) {
3117 i_op2 = ILI_OPND(i_op1, 2);
3118 i_op1 = ILI_OPND(i_op1, 1);
3119 if (i_op1 == r_op1 && ILI_OPC(i_op2) == IL_ACON &&
3120 CONVAL1G(ILI_OPND(i_op2, 1)) == 0 &&
3121 ACONOFFG(ILI_OPND(i_op2, 1)) == size) {
3122 *addr = r_op1;
3123 *nme = NME_NM(ILI_OPND(real, 2));
3124 return;
3125 }
3126 /*
3127 * TBD - can do better to detect subscripted references:
3128 */
3129 }
3130 }
3131 tmp = mkrtemp_cpx_sc(dtype, expb.sc);
3132 *addr = ad_acon(tmp, 0);
3133 *nme = addnme(NT_VAR, tmp, 0, 0);
3134 loc_of(*nme);
3135 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000) && !imag) {
3136 if (dtype == DT_CMPLX)
3137 chk_block(ad4ili(IL_STSCMPLX, real, *addr, *nme, msz));
3138 else
3139 chk_block(ad4ili(IL_STDCMPLX, real, *addr, *nme, msz));
3140 } else {
3141 chk_block(ad4ili(store, real, *addr, addnme(NT_MEM, SPTR_NULL, *nme, 0), msz));
3142 chk_block(ad4ili(store, imag,
3143 ad3ili(IL_AADD, *addr, ad_aconi(size), 0),
3144 addnme(NT_MEM, NOSYM, *nme, size), msz));
3145 }
3146}
3147
3148/**
3149 * \brief get the chain pointer argument from a descriptor.
3150 *
3151 * \param arglnk is a chain of argument ILI for a call-site.
3152 *
3153 * \param sdsc is the descriptor that has the chain pointer.
3154 *
3155 * \return an IL_LDA ili chain that contains the ILI that loads the chain
3156 * pointer from the descriptor.
3157 */
3158static int
3159get_chain_pointer_closure(SPTR sdsc)
3160{
3161 int nme, cp, cp_offset;
3162
3163 if (XBIT(68, 0x1)) {
3164 cp_offset = 72;
3165 } else {
3166 cp_offset = 40;
3167 }
3168 nme = addnme(NT_VAR, sdsc, 0, 0);
3169 if (SCG(sdsc) != SC_DUMMY) {
3170 if (PARREFG(sdsc)) {
3171 /**
3172 * In LLVM, pointer descriptor is not visible in the outlined func.
3173 * Use mk_address() which fetches the uplevel ref
3174 */
3175 int addr = mk_address(sdsc);
3176 int ili = ad2ili(IL_LDA, addr, nme);
3177 cp = ad3ili(IL_AADD, ili, ad_aconi(cp_offset), 0);
3178 } else {
3179 cp = ad_acon(sdsc, cp_offset);
3180 cp = ad2ili(IL_LDA, cp, nme);
3181 }
3182 } else {
3183 SPTR asym = mk_argasym(sdsc);
3184 int addr = mk_address(sdsc);
3185 int ili = ad2ili(IL_LDA, addr, addnme(NT_VAR, asym, 0, 0));
3186 cp = ad3ili(IL_AADD, ili, ad_aconi(cp_offset), 0);
3187 if (!INTERNREFG(sdsc) && !PARREFG(sdsc))
3188 cp = ad2ili(IL_LDA, cp, nme);
3189 }
3190
3191 return cp;
3192}
3193
3194static int
3195add_last_arg(int arglnk, int displnk)
3196{
3197 int i;
3198
3199 if (ILI_OPC(arglnk) == IL_NULL)
3200 return displnk;
3201
3202 for (i = arglnk; i > 0 && ILI_OPC(ILI_OPND(i, 2)) != IL_NULL;
3203 i = ILI_OPND(i, 2)) {
3204 // do nothing
3205 }
3206
3207 ILI_OPND(i, 2) = displnk;
3208 return arglnk;
3209}

3241static bool

3243{
3244 SPTR sym;
3245 if (ILI_OPC(ili) == IL_ACON) {
3246 sym = SymConval1(ILI_SymOPND(ili, 1));
3247 } else if (IL_TYPE(ILI_OPC(ili)) == ILTY_LOAD) {
3248 int op1 = ILI_OPND(ili,1);
3249 if (ILI_OPC(op1) == IL_ACON) {
3250 sym = SymConval1(ILI_SymOPND(op1, 1));
3251 } else {
3252 sym = NME_SYM(ILI_OPND(ili,2));

4311 if (exp_call_sym) {
4312 DTYPE dt;
4313 fptr_iface = exp_call_sym;
4314 switch (STYPEG(fptr_iface)) {
4315 case ST_ENTRY:
4316 case ST_PROC:
4317 break;
4318 default:
4319 dt = DTYPEG(fptr_iface);
4320 if (DTY(dt) == TY_PTR && DTY(DTySeqTyElement(dt)) == TY_PROC) {
4321 fptr_iface = DTyInterface(DTySeqTyElement(dt));
4322 } else {
4323 fptr_iface = SPTR_NULL;
4324 }
4325 break;
4326 }
4327 }
4328 if (func_addr) {
4329 if (!MSCALLG(exp_call_sym))
4330 jsra_mscall_flag = 0;
4331 else
4332 jsra_mscall_flag = 0x1;
4333 if (IS_INTERNAL_PROC_CALL(opc)) {
4334 SPTR sptr_descno = (SPTR) descno;
4335 arglnk = add_last_arg(arglnk, add_arglnk_closure(sptr_descno));
4336 if (XBIT(121, 0x800)) {
4337 gargl = add_last_arg(gargl, add_gargl_closure(sptr_descno));
4338 }
4339 }
4340 ililnk = ad4ili(IL_JSRA, func_addr, arglnk, jsra_mscall_flag, fptr_iface);
4341 if (XBIT(121, 0x800)) {
4342 gjsr = ad4ili(IL_GJSRA, func_addr, gargl, jsra_mscall_flag, fptr_iface);
4343 ILI_ALT(ililnk) = gjsr;
4344 }
4345 } else if (SCG(exp_call_sym) != SC_DUMMY) {
4346 switch (opc) {
4347 case IM_VCALLA:
4348 case IM_CHVFUNCA:
4349 case IM_NCHVFUNCA:
4350 case IM_KVFUNCA:
4351 case IM_LVFUNCA:
4352 case IM_IVFUNCA:
4353 case IM_RVFUNCA:
4354 case IM_DVFUNCA:
4355 case IM_CVFUNCA:
4356 case IM_CDVFUNCA:
4357#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
4358 case IM_CQVFUNCA:
4359#endif
4360 case IM_PVFUNCA: {
4361 SPTR sptr_descno = (SPTR) descno;
4362 ililnk = exp_type_bound_proc_call(exp_call_sym, sptr_descno, vtoff, arglnk);
4363 if (XBIT(121, 0x800)) {
4364 if (!MSCALLG(exp_call_sym))
4365 jsra_mscall_flag = 0;
4366 else
4367 jsra_mscall_flag = 0x1;
4368 gjsr = ad4ili(IL_GJSRA, ILI_OPND(ililnk, 1), gargl, jsra_mscall_flag,
4369 fptr_iface);
4370 ILI_ALT(ililnk) = gjsr;
4371 }
4372 } break;
4373 default:
4374 ililnk = ad2ili(IL_JSR, exp_call_sym, arglnk);
4375 if (XBIT(121, 0x800)) {
4376 gjsr = ad2ili(IL_GJSR, exp_call_sym, gargl);
4377 ILI_ALT(ililnk) = gjsr;
4378 }
4379 }
4380 } else {
4381 SPTR asym = mk_argasym(exp_call_sym);
4382 int addr = mk_address(exp_call_sym);
4383 /* Currently we don't set CONTAINEDG for outlined function - no need too */
4384 if (!((INTERNREFG(exp_call_sym) && CONTAINEDG(gbl.currsub)) ||
4385 (gbl.outlined && PARREFG(exp_call_sym))))
4386 addr = ad2ili(IL_LDA, addr, addnme(NT_VAR, asym, 0, 0));
4387 if (!MSCALLG(exp_call_sym))
4388 jsra_mscall_flag = 0;
4389 else
4390 jsra_mscall_flag = 0x1;
4391
4392 ililnk = ad4ili(IL_JSRA, addr, arglnk, jsra_mscall_flag, fptr_iface);
4393 if (XBIT(121, 0x800)) {
4394 gjsr = ad4ili(IL_GJSRA, addr, gargl, jsra_mscall_flag, fptr_iface);
4395 ILI_ALT(ililnk) = gjsr;
4396 }
4397 }
4398 iltb.callfg = 1;
4399 switch (opc) {
4400 case IM_CALL:
4401 case IM_CHFUNC:
4402 case IM_NCHFUNC:
4403 case IM_CALLA:
4404 case IM_PCALLA:
4405 case IM_VCALLA:
4406 case IM_CHVFUNCA:
4407 case IM_NCHVFUNCA:
4408 case IM_CHFUNCA:
4409 case IM_NCHFUNCA:
4410 case IM_PCHFUNCA:
4411 case IM_PNCHFUNCA:
4412 chk_block(ililnk);
4413 break;
4414 case IM_KFUNC:
4415 case IM_KFUNCA:
4416 case IM_PKFUNCA:
4417 case IM_KVFUNCA:
4418 ililnk = ad2ili(IL_DFRKR, ililnk, KR_RETVAL);
4419 ILI_OF(curilm) = ililnk;
4420 break;
4421 case IM_LFUNC:
4422 case IM_IFUNC:
4423 case IM_LFUNCA:
4424 case IM_IFUNCA:
4425 case IM_PLFUNCA:
4426 case IM_PIFUNCA:
4427 case IM_LVFUNCA:
4428 case IM_IVFUNCA:
4429 ILI_OF(curilm) = ad2ili(IL_DFRIR, ililnk, IR_RETVAL);
4430 break;
4431 case IM_RFUNC:
4432 case IM_RFUNCA:
4433 case IM_PRFUNCA:
4434 case IM_RVFUNCA:
4435 ILI_OF(curilm) = ad2ili(IL_DFRSP, ililnk, FR_RETVAL);
4436 break;
4437 case IM_DFUNC:
4438 case IM_DFUNCA:
4439 case IM_PDFUNCA:
4440 case IM_DVFUNCA:
4441 ILI_OF(curilm) = ad2ili(IL_DFRDP, ililnk, FR_RETVAL);
4442 break;
4443#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
4444 case IM_QFUNC:
4445 case IM_QFUNCA:
4446 case IM_PQFUNCA:
4447 case IM_QVFUNCA:
4448 ILI_OF(curilm) = ad2ili(IL_DFRQP, ililnk, FR_RETVAL);
4449 break;
4450#endif
4451 case IM_CFUNC:
4452 case IM_CFUNCA:
4453 case IM_PCFUNCA:
4454 case IM_CVFUNCA:
4455 chk_block(ililnk);
4456 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000)) {
4457 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDSCMPLX, cfunc, cfunc_nme, MSZ_F8);
4458 } else {
4459 ILM_RRESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDSP, cfunc, addnme(NT_MEM, SPTR_NULL, cfunc_nme, 0), MSZ_F4);
4460 ILM_IRESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDSP, ad3ili(IL_AADD, cfunc, ad_aconi(4), 0), addnme(NT_MEM, NOSYM, cfunc_nme, 4), MSZ_F4);
4461 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISCMPLX;
4462 }
4463
4464 break;
4465 case IM_CDFUNC:
4466 case IM_CDFUNCA:
4467 case IM_PCDFUNCA:
4468 case IM_CDVFUNCA:
4469 chk_block(ililnk);
4470 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000)) {
4471 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDDCMPLX, cfunc, cfunc_nme, MSZ_F16);
4472 } else {
4473 ILM_RRESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDDP, cfunc, addnme(NT_MEM, SPTR_NULL, cfunc_nme, 0), MSZ_F8);
4474 ILM_IRESULT(curilm) =
4475 ad3ili(IL_LDDP, ad3ili(IL_AADD, cfunc, ad_aconi(8), 0),
4476 addnme(NT_MEM, NOSYM, cfunc_nme, 8), MSZ_F8);
4477 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISDCMPLX;
4478 }
4479 break;
4480#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
4481 case IM_CQFUNC:
4482 case IM_CQFUNCA:
4483 case IM_PCQFUNCA:
4484 case IM_CQVFUNCA:
4485 chk_block(ililnk);
4486 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000)) {
4487 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDQCMPLX, cfunc, cfunc_nme, MSZ_F32);
4488 } else {
4489 ILM_RRESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDQP, cfunc, addnme(NT_MEM, SPTR_NULL, cfunc_nme, 0), MSZ_F16);
4490 ILM_IRESULT(curilm) =
4491 ad3ili(IL_LDQP, ad3ili(IL_AADD, cfunc, ad_aconi(16), 0),
4492 addnme(NT_MEM, NOSYM, cfunc_nme, 16), MSZ_F16);
4493 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISQCMPLX;
4494 }
4495 break;
4496#endif
4497 case IM_PFUNC:
4498 case IM_PFUNCA:
4499 case IM_PPFUNCA:
4500 case IM_PVFUNCA:
4501 ILI_OF(curilm) = ad2ili(IL_DFRAR, ililnk, AR_RETVAL);
4502 ILM_NME(curilm) = NME_UNK;
4503 break;
4504 case IM_SFUNC:
4505 if (XBIT(121, 0x800)) {
4506 /* set the result to the JSR so that its result (hidden) argument can be
4507 * replaced:
4508 chk_block(ililnk);
4509 ILI_OF(curilm) = cfunc;
4510 */
4511 ILI_OF(curilm) = ililnk;
4512 ILM_NME(curilm) = cfunc_nme;
4513 break;
4514 }
4515 /* the rest will soon be deleted */
4516 if (retdesc == 1) {
4517 if (sizeof(DTYPEG(exp_call_sym)) <= 4) {
4518 ililnk = ad2ili(IL_DFRIR, ililnk, IR_RETVAL);
4519 ililnk = ad4ili(IL_STKR, ililnk, cfunc, cfunc_nme, MSZ_WORD);
4520 } else {
4521 ililnk = ad2ili(IL_DFRKR, ililnk, KR_RETVAL);
4522 ililnk = ad4ili(IL_STKR, ililnk, cfunc, cfunc_nme, MSZ_I8);
4523 }
4524 chk_block(ililnk);
4525
4526 ILI_OF(curilm) = cfunc;
4527 ILM_NME(curilm) = cfunc_nme;
4528
4529 } else {
4530 /* callee should copy result into hidden argument */
4531 ililnk = ad2ili(IL_DFRAR, ililnk, AR_RETVAL);
4532 ILM_NME(curilm) = cfunc_nme;
4533 }
4534 break;
4535 default:
4536 interr("exp_call: bad function opc", opc, ERR_Severe);
4537 }
4538 end_arg_ili();
4539}

4541/**
4542 \param ext name of routine to call
4543 \param res_dtype function return type
4544
4545 Generate a sequence of ili for the current ilm which is an "arithmetic".
4546 This sequence essentially looks like a normal call, except where we can,
4547 arguments are passed by value.
4548
4549 The requirements are:
4550 1. The ilm looks like an "arithmetic" ILM where there's a fixed number
4551 of operands (determined by the ilms info).
4552 2. The result is returned in a temporary.
4553 3. The address of the result is the first argument in the call.
4554 4. The operands are fully evaluated (no reference ilms).
4555 5. Character arguments are not seen.
4556
4557 For now this only works for complex/double complex ILMs which are QJSRs in
4558 the "standard" fortran.
4559 */
4560void
4561exp_qjsr(const char *ext, DTYPE res_dtype, ILM *ilmp, int curilm)
4562{
4563 int nargs;
4564 int ililnk; /* ili link */
4565 int ilix; /* ili pointer */
4566 ILM *ilmlnk; /* current ILM operand */
4567 int ilm1;
4568 int i; /* temps */
4569 static ainfo_t ainfo;
4570 SPTR res; /* sptr of function result temporary */
4571 int res_addr;
4572 int res_nme;
4573 int extsym;
4574
4575 if (DT_ISCMPLX(res_dtype)) {
4576 res = mkrtemp_arg1_sc(res_dtype, expb.sc);
4577 res_addr = ad_acon(res, 0);
4578 res_nme = addnme(NT_VAR, res, 0, 0);
4579 ADDRTKNP(res, 1);
4580 } else {
4581 interr("exp_qjsr, illegal dtype", res_dtype, ERR_Severe);
4582 return;
4583 }
4584 nargs = ilms[ILM_OPC(ilmp)].oprs;
4585 extsym = mkfunc(ext);
4586#ifdef ARG1PTRP
4587 ARG1PTRP(extsym, 1);
4588#endif
4589 init_ainfo(&ainfo);
4590
4591 i = nargs;
4592 while (nargs--) {
4593 ilm1 = ILM_OPND(ilmp, i);
4594 ilmlnk = (ILM *)(ilmb.ilm_base + ilm1); /* ith operand */
4595 switch (ILM_RESTYPE(ilm1)) {
4596 case ILM_ISCHAR:
4597 interr("exp_qjsr: char arg not allowed", ilm1, ERR_Severe);
4598 break;
4599 case ILM_ISCMPLX:
4600 arg_sp(ILM_IRESULT(ilm1), &ainfo);
4601 arg_sp(ILM_RRESULT(ilm1), &ainfo);
4602 break;
4603 case ILM_ISDCMPLX:
4604 arg_dp(ILM_IRESULT(ilm1), &ainfo);
4605 arg_dp(ILM_RRESULT(ilm1), &ainfo);
4606 break;
4607 default:
4608 ilix = ILM_RESULT(ilm1);
4609 switch (IL_RES(ILI_OPC(ilix))) {
4610 case ILIA_IR:
4611 arg_ir(ilix, &ainfo);
4612 break;
4613 case ILIA_AR:
4614 arg_ar(ilix, &ainfo, 0);
4615 break;
4616 case ILIA_SP:
4617 arg_sp(ilix, &ainfo);
4618 break;
4619 case ILIA_DP:
4620 arg_dp(ilix, &ainfo);
4621 break;
4622 case ILIA_KR:
4623 arg_kr(ilix, &ainfo);
4624 break;
4625#ifdef ILIA_CS
4626 case ILIA_CS:
4627 ilix = ad1ili(IL_SCMPLX2IMAG, ILM_RESULT(ilm1));
4628 arg_sp(ilix, &ainfo);
4629 ilix = ad1ili(IL_SCMPLX2REAL, ILM_RESULT(ilm1));
4630 arg_sp(ilix, &ainfo);
4631 break;
4632 case ILIA_CD:
4633 ilix = ad1ili(IL_DCMPLX2IMAG, ILM_RESULT(ilm1));
4634 arg_dp(ilix, &ainfo);
4635 ilix = ad1ili(IL_DCMPLX2REAL, ILM_RESULT(ilm1));
4636 arg_dp(ilix, &ainfo);
4637 break;
4638#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
4639 case ILIA_CQ:
4640 ilix = ad1ili(IL_QCMPLX2IMAG, ILM_RESULT(ilm1));
4641 arg_qp(ilix, &ainfo);
4642 ilix = ad1ili(IL_QCMPLX2REAL, ILM_RESULT(ilm1));
4643 arg_qp(ilix, &ainfo);
4644 break;
4645#endif
4646#endif
4647 default:
4648 interr("exp_qjsr: ili ret type not cased", ilix, ERR_Severe);
4649 break;
4650 }
4651 }
4652 i--;
4653 } /* for each arg */
4654
4655 arg_ar(res_addr, &ainfo, 0);
4656 ililnk = ad2ili(IL_JSR, extsym, ainfo.lnk);
4657 iltb.callfg = 1;
4658 chk_block(ililnk);
4659
4660 if (res_dtype == DT_CMPLX) {
4661 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000)) {
4662 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDSCMPLX, res_addr, res_nme, MSZ_F8);
4663 } else {
4664 ILM_RRESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDSP, res_addr, addnme(NT_MEM, SPTR_NULL, res_nme, 0), MSZ_F4);
4665 ILM_IRESULT(curilm) =
4666 ad3ili(IL_LDSP, ad3ili(IL_AADD, res_addr, ad_aconi(4), 0),
4667 addnme(NT_MEM, NOSYM, res_nme, 4), MSZ_F4);
4668 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISCMPLX;
4669 }
4670#ifdef TARGET_SUPPORTS_QUADFP
4671 } else if (res_dtype == DT_QCMPLX) {
4672 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000)) {
4673 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDQCMPLX, res_addr, res_nme, MSZ_F32);
4674 } else {
4675 ILM_RRESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDQP, res_addr, addnme(NT_MEM, SPTR_NULL, res_nme, 0), MSZ_F16);
4676 ILM_IRESULT(curilm) =
4677 ad3ili(IL_LDQP, ad3ili(IL_AADD, res_addr, ad_aconi(16), 0),
4678 addnme(NT_MEM, NOSYM, res_nme, 16), MSZ_F16);
4679 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISQCMPLX;
4680 }
4681#endif
4682 } else {
4683 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000)) {
4684 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDDCMPLX, res_addr, res_nme, MSZ_F16);
4685 } else {
4686
4687 ILM_RRESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDDP, res_addr, addnme(NT_MEM, SPTR_NULL, res_nme, 0), MSZ_F8);
4688 ILM_IRESULT(curilm) =
4689 ad3ili(IL_LDDP, ad3ili(IL_AADD, res_addr, ad_aconi(8), 0),
4690 addnme(NT_MEM, NOSYM, res_nme, 8), MSZ_F8);
4691 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISDCMPLX;
4692 }
4693 }
4694
4695 end_ainfo(&ainfo);
4696}

4698/**
4699 \param ext name of routine to call
4700 \param res_dtype function return type
4701
4702 Same as exp_qjsr() except that if the result is complex, its pointer argument
4703 is passed as the last argument instead of the first argument. This is
4704 necessary to keep double arguments properly aligned on the stack.
4705
4706 For now this only works for complex/double complex ILMs which are QJSRs in
4707 the "standard" fortran.
4708 */
4709void
4710exp_zqjsr(char *ext, DTYPE res_dtype, ILM *ilmp, int curilm)
4711{
4712 int nargs;
4713 int ililnk; /* ili link */
4714 int ilix; /* ili pointer */
4715 ILM *ilmlnk; /* current ILM operand */
4716 int ilm1;
4717 int i; /* temps */
4718 static ainfo_t ainfo;
4719 SPTR res; /* sptr of function result temporary */
4720 int res_addr;
4721 int res_nme;
4722 int extsym;
4723
4724 if (DT_ISCMPLX(res_dtype)) {
4725 res = mkrtemp_cpx_sc(res_dtype, expb.sc);
4726 res_addr = ad_acon(res, 0);
4727 res_nme = addnme(NT_VAR, res, 0, 0);
4728 ADDRTKNP(res, 1);
4729 } else {
4730 interr("exp_zqjsr, illegal dtype", res_dtype, ERR_Severe);
4731 return;
4732 }
4733 nargs = ilms[ILM_OPC(ilmp)].oprs;
4734 extsym = mkfunc(ext);
4735 init_ainfo(&ainfo);
4736 arg_ar(res_addr, &ainfo, 0);
4737
4738 i = nargs;
4739 while (nargs--) {
4740 ilm1 = ILM_OPND(ilmp, i);
4741 ilmlnk = (ILM *)(ilmb.ilm_base + ilm1); /* ith operand */
4742 switch (ILM_RESTYPE(ilm1)) {
4743 case ILM_ISCHAR:
4744 interr("exp_zqjsr: char arg not allowed", ilm1, ERR_Severe);
4745 break;
4746 case ILM_ISCMPLX:
4747 arg_sp(ILM_IRESULT(ilm1), &ainfo);
4748 arg_sp(ILM_RRESULT(ilm1), &ainfo);
4749 break;
4750 case ILM_ISDCMPLX:
4751 arg_dp(ILM_IRESULT(ilm1), &ainfo);
4752 arg_dp(ILM_RRESULT(ilm1), &ainfo);
4753 break;
4754 default:
4755 ilix = ILM_RESULT(ilm1);
4756 switch (IL_RES(ILI_OPC(ilix))) {
4757 case ILIA_IR:
4758 arg_ir(ilix, &ainfo);
4759 break;
4760 case ILIA_AR:
4761 arg_ar(ilix, &ainfo, 0);
4762 break;
4763 case ILIA_SP:
4764 arg_sp(ilix, &ainfo);
4765 break;
4766 case ILIA_DP:
4767 arg_dp(ilix, &ainfo);
4768 break;
4769 case ILIA_KR:
4770 arg_kr(ilix, &ainfo);
4771 break;
4772#ifdef ILIA_CS
4773 case ILIA_CS:
4774 ilix = ad1ili(IL_SCMPLX2IMAG, ILM_RESULT(ilm1));
4775 arg_sp(ilix, &ainfo);
4776 ilix = ad1ili(IL_SCMPLX2REAL, ILM_RESULT(ilm1));
4777 arg_sp(ilix, &ainfo);
4778 break;
4779 case ILIA_CD:
4780 ilix = ad1ili(IL_DCMPLX2IMAG, ILM_RESULT(ilm1));
4781 arg_dp(ilix, &ainfo);
4782 ilix = ad1ili(IL_DCMPLX2REAL, ILM_RESULT(ilm1));
4783 arg_dp(ilix, &ainfo);
4784 break;
4785#endif
4786 default:
4787 interr("exp_zqjsr: ili ret type not cased", ilix, ERR_Severe);
4788 break;
4789 }
4790 }
4791 i--;
4792 } /* for each arg */
4793
4794 ililnk = ad2ili(IL_JSR, extsym, ainfo.lnk);
4795 iltb.callfg = 1;
4796 chk_block(ililnk);
4797
4798 if (res_dtype == DT_CMPLX) {
4799 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000)) {
4800 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDSCMPLX, res_addr, res_nme, MSZ_F8);
4801 } else {
4802
4803 ILM_RRESULT(curilm) =
4804 ad3ili(IL_LDSP, res_addr, addnme(NT_MEM, SPTR_NULL, res_nme, 0), MSZ_F4);
4805 ILM_IRESULT(curilm) =
4806 ad3ili(IL_LDSP, ad3ili(IL_AADD, res_addr, ad_aconi(4), 0),
4807 addnme(NT_MEM, NOSYM, res_nme, 4), MSZ_F4);
4808 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISCMPLX;
4809 }
4810 } else {
4811 if (XBIT(70, 0x40000000)) {
4812 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDDCMPLX, res_addr, res_nme, MSZ_F16);
4813 } else {
4814 ILM_RRESULT(curilm) =
4815 ad3ili(IL_LDDP, res_addr, addnme(NT_MEM, SPTR_NULL, res_nme, 0), MSZ_F8);
4816 ILM_IRESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LDDP, ad3ili(IL_AADD, res_addr, ad_aconi(8), 0),
4817 addnme(NT_MEM, NOSYM, res_nme, 8), MSZ_F8);
4818 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISDCMPLX;
4819 }
4820 }
4821
4822 end_ainfo(&ainfo);
4823}

4884/** Expand an smove ILM.
4885 \param destilm: ilm of receiving struct/union
4886 \param srcilm: ilm of sending struct/union
4887 \param dtype: data type of struct/union
4888 */
4889void
4890expand_smove(int destilm, int srcilm, DTYPE dtype)
4891{
4892 int dest_nme; /* names entry */
4893 int src_nme; /* names entry */
4894 int dest_addr; /* pointer to ili for destination addr */
4895 int src_addr; /* pointer to ili for source addr */
4896
4897 dest_nme = NME_OF(destilm);
4898 src_nme = NME_OF(srcilm);
4899 if (flg.opt > 1) {
4900 loc_of(dest_nme); /* implicit LOC */
4901 loc_of(src_nme);
4902 }
4903 dest_addr = ILI_OF(destilm);
4904 src_addr = ILI_OF(srcilm);
4905 if (USE_GSMOVE) {
4906 int ilix;
4907 ilix = ad5ili(IL_GSMOVE, src_addr, dest_addr, src_nme, dest_nme, dtype);
4908 chk_block(ilix);
4909 } else {
4910 _exp_smove(dest_nme, src_nme, dest_addr, src_addr, dtype);
4911 }
4912}
4913
4914/** \brief Transform the GSMOVE ILI created by expand_smove()
4915 */
4916void
4917exp_remove_gsmove(void)
4918{
4919 int bihx, iltx, ilix;
4920 p_chk_block = gsmove_chk_block;
4921 for (bihx = gbl.entbih; bihx; bihx = BIH_NEXT(bihx)) {
4922 int next_ilt;
4923 bool any_gsmove = false;
4924 rdilts(bihx);
4925 for (iltx = ILT_NEXT(0); iltx;) {
4926 next_ilt = ILT_NEXT(iltx);
4927 ilix = ILT_ILIP(iltx);
4928 if (ILI_OPC(ilix) == IL_GSMOVE) {
4929 int src_addr = ILI_OPND(ilix, 1);
4930 int dest_addr = ILI_OPND(ilix, 2);
4931 int src_nme = ILI_OPND(ilix, 3);
4932 int dest_nme = ILI_OPND(ilix, 4);
4933 DTYPE dtype = ILI_DTyOPND(ilix, 5);
4934 any_gsmove = true;
4935 gsmove_ilt = iltx;
4936 _exp_smove(dest_nme, src_nme, dest_addr, src_addr, dtype);
4937 ILT_NEXT(gsmove_ilt) = next_ilt;
4938 ILT_PREV(next_ilt) = gsmove_ilt;
4939 delilt(iltx);
4940 }
4941 iltx = next_ilt;
4942 }
4943 wrilts(bihx);
4944 if (DBGBIT(10, 2) && any_gsmove) {
4945 fprintf(gbl.dbgfil, "\n***** After remove gsmove *****\n");
4946 dump_one_block(gbl.dbgfil, bihx, NULL);
4947 }
4948 }
4949 p_chk_block = chk_block;
4950}
4951
4952static void
4953_exp_smove(int dest_nme, int src_nme, int dest_addr, int src_addr, DTYPE dtype)
4954{
4955 ISZ_T n; /* number of bytes left to copy */
4956 int i;
4957 INT offset; /* number of bytes from begin addr */
4958
4959 n = size_of(dtype);
4960 if (0 && !XBIT(2, 0x1000000)) {
4961 chk_block(ad5ili(IL_SMOVEJ, src_addr, dest_addr, src_nme, dest_nme, n));
4962 smove_flag = 1; /* structure move in this function */
4963 return;
4964 }
4965 offset = 0;
4966
4967/* for large structs, copy as much as possible using an smovl/smoveq instr: */
4968#define SMOVE_CHUNK 8
4969#define TEST_BOUND 96
4970 if (n > TEST_BOUND) {
4971
4972 if (XBIT(2, 0x200000)) {
4973 p_chk_block(ad4ili(IL_SMOVE, src_addr, dest_addr,
4974 ad_aconi(n / SMOVE_CHUNK), dest_nme));
4975 } else {
4976 p_chk_block(ad5ili(IL_SMOVEJ, src_addr, dest_addr, src_nme,
4977 dest_nme, n));
4978 }
4979 smove_flag = 1; /* structure move in this function */
4980 offset = (n / SMOVE_CHUNK) * SMOVE_CHUNK;
4981 n = n - offset;
4982 if (n > 0) {
4983 /* add CSE's to prevent addresses from being recalculated: */
4984 src_addr = ad1ili(IL_CSEAR, src_addr);
4985 dest_addr = ad1ili(IL_CSEAR, dest_addr);
4986 }
4987 }
4988
4989 /* generate loads and stores for the parts of the structs remaining: */
4990
4991#define START_AT 0 /* loop for skip size == 8, 4, 2, 1 */
4992 for (i = START_AT; i < 4; i++) {
4993 static struct {
4994 short siz;
4995 short skip;
4996 } info[4] = {{MSZ_I8, 8}, {MSZ_WORD, 4}, {MSZ_UHWORD, 2}, {MSZ_UBYTE, 1}};
4997
4998 int siz = info[i].siz;
4999 int skip = info[i].skip;
5000
5001 while (n >= skip) {
5002 int ilip, ilix; /* temporary ili pointers */
5003
5004 /* add load and store ili: */
5005
5006 ilip = ad_aconi(offset);
5007 ilix = ad3ili(IL_AADD, src_addr, ilip, 0);
5008 if (siz == MSZ_I8)
5009 ilix = ad3ili(IL_LDKR, ilix, src_nme, siz);
5010 else
5011 ilix = ad3ili(IL_LD, ilix, src_nme, siz);
5012 ilip = ad3ili(IL_AADD, dest_addr, ilip, 0);
5013 if (siz == MSZ_I8)
5014 ilip = ad4ili(IL_STKR, ilix, ilip, dest_nme, siz);
5015 else
5016 ilip = ad4ili(IL_ST, ilix, ilip, dest_nme, siz);
5017 p_chk_block(ilip);
5018
5019 offset += skip;
5020 n -= skip;
5021 if (n > 0) {
5022 src_addr = ad1ili(IL_CSEAR, src_addr);
5023 dest_addr = ad1ili(IL_CSEAR, dest_addr);
5024 }
5025 }
5026 }
5027}

5031/**
5032 \param to ilm of receiving struct/union
5033 \param from ilm of sending struct/union
5034 \param dtype data type of struct/union
5035 */
5036void
5037exp_szero(ILM *ilmp, int curilm, int to, int from, int dtype)
5038{
5039 int nme; /* names entry */
5040 int addr, /* address ili where value stored */
5041 expr, /* ili of value being stored */
5042 sym; /* ST item */
5043 int tmp;
5044
5045 nme = NME_OF(to);
5046 addr = ILI_OF(to);
5047 expr = ILI_OF(from);
5048 loc_of(nme);
5049 tmp = ad1ili(IL_NULL, 0);
5050 tmp = ad3ili(IL_ARGAR, addr, tmp, 0);
5051 tmp = ad2ili(IL_ARGIR, expr, tmp);
5052 sym = mkfunc("__c_bzero");
5053 chk_block(ad2ili(IL_JSR, sym, tmp)); /* temporary */
5054}

5056void
5057exp_fstring(ILM_OP opc, ILM *ilmp, int curilm)
5058{
5059 int ili1;
5060 int sym;
5061 int op1, op2;
5062 int tmp;
5063 INT val[2];
5064 int addr, highsub, lowsub;
5065 int hsubili, lsubili;
5066 bool any_kr;
5067 STRDESC *str1, *str2;
5068 int ilm1;
5069
5070 switch (opc) {
5071 case IM_ICHAR: /* char to integer */
5072 tmp = MSZ_BYTE;
5073 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
5074 case IM_INCHAR: /* nchar to integer */
5075 if (opc == IM_INCHAR)
5076 tmp = MSZ_UHWORD;
5077 ilm1 = ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1);
5078 str1 = getstr(ilm1);
5079 if (!str1->next)
5080 ili1 = ILI_OF(ilm1); /* char result */
5081 else {
5082 if (str1->liscon && str1->lval >= 1) {
5083 ;
5084 } else {
5085 str1 = storechartmp(str1, ILM_MXLEN(ilm1), ILM_CLEN(ilm1));
5086 }
5087 ili1 = getstraddr(str1);
5088 }
5089 if (ILI_OPC(ili1) == IL_ACON && opc != IM_INCHAR &&
5090 STYPEG(sym = CONVAL1G(ILI_OPND(ili1, 1))) == ST_CONST) {
5091/* constant char str */
5092#if DEBUG
5093 assert(DTY(DTYPEG(sym)) == TY_CHAR, "non char op of ICHAR", ili1,
5094 ERR_Severe);
5095#endif
5096 op1 = CONVAL1G(sym); /* names area idx containing string */
5097 op2 = CONVAL2G(ILI_OPND(ili1, 1)); /* offset */
5098 tmp = stb.n_base[op1 + op2] & 0xff;
5099 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad_icon(tmp);
5100 } else
5101 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_LD, ili1, NME_STR1, tmp);
5102 return;
5103
5104 case IM_CHAR: /* integer to char */
5105 val[0] = getchartmp(ad_icon(1));
5106 val[1] = 0;
5107 tmp = getcon(val, DT_ADDR);
5108 op1 = ILI_OF(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1));
5109 if (IL_RES(ILI_OPC(op1)) == ILIA_KR)
5110 op1 = ad1ili(IL_KIMV, op1);
5111 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_ST, op1, ad1ili(IL_ACON, tmp), NME_STR1, MSZ_BYTE);
5112 chk_block(ili1);
5113 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad1ili(IL_ACON, tmp);
5114 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISCHAR;
5115 if (CHARLEN_64BIT) {
5116 ILM_CLEN(curilm) = ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = ad_kconi(1);
5117 } else {
5118 ILM_CLEN(curilm) = ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = ad_icon(1);
5119 }
5120 return;
5121
5122 case IM_NCHAR: /* integer to kanji char */
5123 val[0] = getchartmp(ad_icon(2));
5124 val[1] = 0;
5125 tmp = getcon(val, DT_ADDR);
5126 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_ST, ILI_OF(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1)), ad1ili(IL_ACON, tmp),
5127 NME_STR1, MSZ_UHWORD);
5128 chk_block(ili1);
5129 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad1ili(IL_ACON, tmp);
5130 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISCHAR;
5131 if (CHARLEN_64BIT) {
5132 ILM_CLEN(curilm) = ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = ad_kconi(1);
5133 } else {
5134 ILM_CLEN(curilm) = ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = ad_icon(1);
5135 }
5136 return;
5137
5138 case IM_SST: /* string store */
5139 case IM_NSST:
5140 str1 = getstr(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1));
5141 str2 = getstr(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 2));
5142#if DEBUG
5143 assert(str1->cnt == 1, "string store into concat", curilm, ERR_Severe);
5144#endif
5145 /* special case string store into single char */
5146 if (strislen1(str1)) {
5147 int tmp = MSZ_BYTE;
5148 if (strislen0(str2)) {
5149 if (opc != IM_NSST) {
5150 str2 = getstrconst(" ", 1);
5151 } else {
5152 goto bldfcall;
5153 }
5154 }
5155 if (opc == IM_NSST)
5156 tmp = MSZ_UHWORD;
5157 ili1 = ad3ili(IL_LD, getstraddr(str2), NME_STR1, tmp);
5158 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_ST, ili1, getstraddr(str1), NME_STR1, tmp);
5159 chk_block(ili1);
5160 return;
5161 }
5162 bldfcall:
5163 /* build function call */
5164 ili1 = exp_strcpy(str1, str2);
5165 iltb.callfg = 1;
5166 chk_block(ili1);
5167 return;
5168
5169 case IM_SPSEUDOST: /* string pseudo store */
5170 case IM_NSPSEUDOST:
5171 /* for now, just force the character expression into a temporary
5172 * and pass on the information for the temp.
5173 */
5174 str2 = getstr(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 2));
5175 ili1 = ad_icon(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1));
5176 str1 = storechartmp(str2, ili1, ili1);
5177 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = getstraddr(str1);
5178 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISCHAR;
5179 if (CHARLEN_64BIT) {
5180 ILM_CLEN(curilm) = ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = sel_iconv(ili1, 1);
5181 } else {
5182 ILM_CLEN(curilm) = ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = ili1;
5183 }
5184 return;
5185
5186 case IM_LEN: /* length of string */
5187 case IM_NLEN:
5188 ili1 = ILM_CLEN(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1));
5189 if (IL_RES(ILI_OPC(ili1)) == ILIA_KR)
5190 ili1 = ad1ili(IL_KIMV, ili1);
5191 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ili1;
5192#if DEBUG
5193 assert(ILM_RESULT(curilm) != 0, "IM_LEN:len ili 0", curilm, ERR_Severe);
5194#endif
5195 return;
5196 case IM_KLEN: /* length of string */
5197 ili1 = ILM_CLEN(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1));
5198 if (IL_RES(ILI_OPC(ili1)) != ILIA_KR)
5199 ili1 = ad1ili(IL_IKMV, ili1);
5200 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ili1;
5201 return;
5202
5203 case IM_SUBS: /* substring */
5204 case IM_NSUBS:
5205 /*-
5206 * addr = addr + lowsub - 1
5207 * len = highsub - lowsub + 1
5208 * maxlen = len (if const.) else maxlen
5209 */
5210 addr = ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1);
5211 lowsub = ILM_OPND(ilmp, 2);
5212 highsub = ILM_OPND(ilmp, 3);
5213 lsubili = ILI_OF(lowsub);
5214 hsubili = ILI_OF(highsub);
5215
5216 if (CHARLEN_64BIT)
5217 any_kr = true;
5218 else
5219 any_kr = (IL_RES(ILI_OPC(lsubili)) == ILIA_KR) ||
5220 (IL_RES(ILI_OPC(hsubili)) == ILIA_KR);
5221 if (any_kr) {
5222 if (IL_RES(ILI_OPC(lsubili)) != ILIA_KR)
5223 lsubili = ad1ili(IL_IKMV, lsubili);
5224 if (IL_RES(ILI_OPC(hsubili)) != ILIA_KR)
5225 hsubili = ad1ili(IL_IKMV, hsubili);
5226 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_KSUB, lsubili, ad_kconi(1));
5227 if (opc == IM_NSUBS)
5228 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_KMUL, ili1, ad_kconi(2));
5229 ili1 = ad1ili(IL_KAMV, ili1);
5230 ILI_OF(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_AADD, ILI_OF(addr), ili1, 0);
5231 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_KSUB, hsubili, lsubili);
5232 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_KADD, ili1, ad_kconi(1));
5233 if (!CHARLEN_64BIT)
5234 ili1 = ad1ili(IL_KIMV, ili1);
5235 } else {
5236 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_ISUB, lsubili, ad_icon(1));
5237 if (opc == IM_NSUBS)
5238 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_IMUL, ili1, ad_icon(2));
5239 ili1 = ad1ili(IL_IAMV, ili1);
5240 ILI_OF(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_AADD, ILI_OF(addr), ili1, 0);
5241 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_ISUB, hsubili, lsubili);
5242 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_IADD, ili1, ad_icon(1));
5243 if (CHARLEN_64BIT)
5244 ili1 = sel_iconv(ili1, 1);
5245 }
5246
5247 if (IL_TYPE(ILI_OPC(ili1)) == ILTY_CONS) {
5248 if (get_isz_cval(ILI_OPND(ili1, 1)) < 0)
5249 ili1 = ad_icon(0);
5250 if (CHARLEN_64BIT)
5251 ili1 = sel_iconv(ili1, 1);
5252 ILM_CLEN(curilm) = ili1;
5253 ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = ili1;
5254 } else {
5255 if (CHARLEN_64BIT) {
5256 ILM_CLEN(curilm) = ad2ili(IL_KMAX, ili1, ad_kconi(0));
5257 if (ILM_MXLEN(addr))
5258 ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = sel_iconv(ILM_MXLEN(addr), 1);
5259 else
5260 ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = 0;
5261 } else {
5262 ILM_CLEN(curilm) = ad2ili(IL_IMAX, ili1, ad_icon(0));
5263 ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = ILM_MXLEN(addr);
5264 }
5265 }
5266 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISCHAR;
5267 return;
5268
5269 case IM_SCAT: /* concatenation */
5270 case IM_NSCAT:
5271 op1 = ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1);
5272 op2 = ILM_OPND(ilmp, 2);
5273 if (CHARLEN_64BIT) {
5274 ILM_CLEN(curilm) = ad2ili(IL_KADD, sel_iconv(ILM_CLEN(op1), 1),
5275 sel_iconv(ILM_CLEN(op2), 1));
5276 } else {
5277 ILM_CLEN(curilm) =
5278 ad2ili(IL_IADD, ILM_CLEN(op1), ILM_CLEN(op2));
5279 }
5280 if (ILM_MXLEN(op1) && ILM_MXLEN(op2)) {
5281 if (CHARLEN_64BIT) {
5282 ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = ad2ili(IL_KADD, sel_iconv(ILM_MXLEN(op1), 1),
5283 sel_iconv(ILM_MXLEN(op2), 1));
5284 } else {
5285 ILM_MXLEN(curilm) =
5286 ad2ili(IL_IADD, ILM_MXLEN(op1), ILM_MXLEN(op2));
5287 }
5288 } else {
5289 ILM_MXLEN(curilm) = 0;
5290 }
5291 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = 0; /* FIXME? */
5292 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISCHAR;
5293 return;
5294
5295 case IM_SCMP:
5296 case IM_NSCMP:
5297 /* set indicator for the referencing relational ILM --
5298 * indicates a string compare is handled by calling
5299 * ftn_strcmp.
5300 */
5301 ILM_RESTYPE(curilm) = ILM_ISCHAR;
5302 FLANG_FALLTHROUGH;
5303 case IM_INDEX:
5304 case IM_KINDEX:
5305 case IM_NINDEX:
5306 /* if either arg is SCAT generate tmp and store into it */
5307 str1 = getstr(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1));
5308 if (str1->next)
5309 str1 = storechartmp(str1, ILM_MXLEN(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1)),
5310 ILM_CLEN(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1)));
5311 str2 = getstr(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 2));
5312 if (str2->next)
5313 str2 = storechartmp(str2, ILM_MXLEN(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 2)),
5314 ILM_CLEN(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 2)));
5315 if (opc == IM_SCMP) {
5316 char *p1, *p2;
5317
5318 p1 = getcharconst(str1);
5319 p2 = getcharconst(str2);
5320 if (p1 != NULL & p2 != NULL) {
5321 val[0] = ftn_strcmp(p1, p2, str1->lval, str2->lval);
5322 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad_icon(val[0]);
5323 return;
5324 }
5325 if (strislen1(str1) && strislen1(str2)) {
5326 /* special case str cmp of single chars: generate a ICMP ili
5327 * with a load the two character items. This ili is save as
5328 * the result of the SCMP and will be picked up as a special
5329 * case by the relational ILM referencing this ILM (due to the
5330 * ILM_RESTYPE of ILM_ISCHAR).
5331 */
5332 op1 = ad3ili(IL_LD, getstraddr(str1), NME_STR1, MSZ_BYTE);
5333 op2 = ad3ili(IL_LD, getstraddr(str2), NME_STR1, MSZ_BYTE);
5334 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ad3ili(IL_ICMP, op1, op2, CC_EQ);
5335 return;
5336 }
5337 }
5338 /* gen call to strcmp or stridx routine */
5339 iltb.callfg = 1;
5340 ili1 = exp_strx(opc, str1, str2);
5341 ILM_RESULT(curilm) = ili1;
5342 return;
5343
5344 default:
5345 interr("unrecognized fstr ILM", opc, ERR_Severe);
5346 break;
5347 }
5348}
5349
5350static int
5351exp_strx(int opc, STRDESC *str1, STRDESC *str2)
5352{
5353 int sym;
5354 int ili1;
5355 const char *str_index_nm;
5356 const char *nstr_index_nm;
5357 const char *strcmp_nm;
5358 const char *nstrcmp_nm;
5359 const char *ftn_str_kindex_nm;
5360
5361 if (CHARLEN_64BIT) {
5362 str_index_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_str_index_klen);
5363 nstr_index_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_nstr_index_klen);
5364 strcmp_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_strcmp_klen);
5365 nstrcmp_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_nstrcmp_klen);
5366 ftn_str_kindex_nm = "ftn_str_kindex_klen";
5367 } else {
5368 str_index_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_str_index);
5369 nstr_index_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_nstr_index);
5370 strcmp_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_strcmp);
5371 nstrcmp_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_nstrcmp);
5372 ftn_str_kindex_nm = "ftn_str_kindex";
5373 }
5374
5375 if (str1->dtype == TY_NCHAR)
5376 sym = frte_func(mkfunc, opc == IM_NSCMP ? nstrcmp_nm : nstr_index_nm);
5377 else if (opc == IM_KINDEX)
5378 sym = mkfunc(ftn_str_kindex_nm);
5379 else
5380 sym = frte_func(mkfunc, opc == IM_SCMP ? strcmp_nm : str_index_nm);
5381 ili1 = ad1ili(IL_NULL, 0);
5382 /* str1 & str2 lens */
5383 if (!XBIT(125, 0x40000)) {
5384 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_ARGKR, getstrlen64(str2), ili1);
5385 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_ARGKR, getstrlen64(str1), ili1);
5386 } else {
5387 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_ARGIR, getstrlen(str2), ili1);
5388 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_ARGIR, getstrlen(str1), ili1);
5389 }
5390 /* str1 & str2 addrs */
5391 ili1 = ad3ili(IL_ARGAR, getstraddr(str2), ili1, 0);
5392 ili1 = ad3ili(IL_ARGAR, getstraddr(str1), ili1, 0);
5393 /* JSR */
5394 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_JSR, sym, ili1);
5395 if (opc == IM_KINDEX)
5396 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_DFRKR, ili1, KR_RETVAL);
5397 else
5398 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_DFRIR, ili1, IR_RETVAL);
5399 return ili1;
5400}

5409}

5411static int
5412exp_strcpy(STRDESC *str1, STRDESC *str2)
5413{
5414 int sym;
5415 int n;
5416 int ili1;
5417 static ainfo_t ainfo;
5418 const char *str_copy_nm;
5419 const char *nstr_copy_nm;
5420 if (CHARLEN_64BIT) {
5421 str_copy_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_str_copy_klen);
5422 nstr_copy_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_nstr_copy_klen);
5423 } else {
5424 str_copy_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_str_copy);
5425 nstr_copy_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_nstr_copy);
5426 }
5427
5428 init_ainfo(&ainfo);
5429
5430 if (str1->dtype == TY_CHAR) {
5431 if (!strovlp(str1, str2)) {
5432/*
5433 * single source, no overlap
5434 */
5435#define STR_MOVE_THRESH 16
5436 if (!XBIT(125, 0x800) && str1->liscon && str2->liscon &&
5437 str1->lval <= STR_MOVE_THRESH) {
5438 /*
5439 * perform a 'block move' of the rhs to the lhs -- the move
5440 * will move a combination of 8 (64-bit only) 4, 2, and 1
5441 * bytes. Note that this same code appears in the 32-bit
5442 * and 64-bit compilers, thus the check of TARGET_X8632.
5443 */
5444 if (str1->lval > str2->lval) {
5445 char *p2;
5446 p2 = getcharconst(str2);
5447 if (p2) {
5448 /*
5449 * if the rhs is a constant shorter than the lhs,
5450 * need to create a new constant padded with
5451 * blanks. Pad the constant to make its length
5452 * a multiple of a number specific to the arch
5453 * (8 for 64-bit, and 4 for 32-bit).
5454 */
5455 ISZ_T len;
5456 ISZ_T md;
5457 ISZ_T pad;
5458 char b[STR_MOVE_THRESH + 1];
5459 char *str;
5460
5461 str = b;
5462 len = (ISZ_T)str2->lval;
5463 while (len-- > 0) {
5464 *str++ = *p2++;
5465 }
5466 md = (8 - (str2->lval & 0x7)) & 0x7;
5467 if (XBIT(125, 0x1000) || str2->lval + md > str1->lval) {
5468 pad = str1->lval - str2->lval;
5469 } else {
5470 pad = md;
5471 }
5472 len = str2->lval + pad;
5473 while (pad-- > 0) {
5474 *str++ = ' ';
5475 }
5476 str2 = getstrconst(b, len);
5477 }
5478 }
5479 ili1 = block_str_move(str1, str2);
5480 return ili1;
5481 }
5482 sym = frte_func(mkfunc_cncall, mkRteRtnNm(RTE_str_cpy1));
5483
5484 /* from addr and length */
5485 arg_length(str2, &ainfo);
5486 arg_ar(getstraddr(str2), &ainfo, 0);
5487
5488 /* to addr and length */
5489 arg_length(str1, &ainfo);
5490 arg_ar(getstraddr(str1), &ainfo, 0);
5491
5492 /* JSR */
5493 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_JSR, sym, ainfo.lnk);
5494 end_ainfo(&ainfo);
5495 return ili1;
5496 }
5497 }
5498
5499 if (str1->dtype == TY_NCHAR)
5500 sym = frte_func(mkfunc, nstr_copy_nm);
5501 else
5502 sym = frte_func(mkfunc, str_copy_nm);
5503 VARARGP(sym, 1);
5504 n = str2->cnt;
5505
5506 /* from addrs and lengths, need to recurse */
5507 from_addr_and_length(str2, &ainfo);
5508
5509 /* to addr and length */
5510 arg_length(str1, &ainfo);
5511 arg_ar(getstraddr(str1), &ainfo, 0);
5512
5513 arg_ir(ad_icon(n), &ainfo); /* # from strings */
5514 /* JSR */
5515 ili1 = ad2ili(IL_JSR, sym, ainfo.lnk);
5516 end_ainfo(&ainfo);
5517 return ili1;
5518}
5519
5520static int
5521block_str_move(STRDESC *str1, STRDESC *str2)
5522{
5523 int len;
5524 int bfill;
5525 int nb;
5526 ISZ_T off;
5527 int addr1, addr2;
5528 int a1, a2;
5529 int ili1;
5530
5531 ili1 = 0;
5532 len = str1->lval;
5533 if (len <= str2->lval)
5534 bfill = 0;
5535 else {
5536 bfill = len - str2->lval;
5537 len = str2->lval;
5538 }
5539 addr1 = getstraddr(str1);
5540 addr2 = getstraddr(str2);
5541 off = 0;
5542 while (true) {
5543 if (ili1)
5544 chk_block(ili1);
5545 if (len > 7) {
5546 nb = 8;
5547 } else if (len > 3) {
5548 nb = 4;
5549 } else if (len > 1) {
5550 nb = 2;
5551 } else {
5552 nb = 1;
5553 }
5554 a1 = ad3ili(IL_AADD, addr1, ad_aconi(off), 0);
5555 a2 = ad3ili(IL_AADD, addr2, ad_aconi(off), 0);
5556 switch (nb) {
5557 case 8:
5558 ili1 = ad3ili(IL_LDKR, a2, NME_STR1, MSZ_I8);
5559 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_STKR, ili1, a1, NME_STR1, MSZ_I8);
5560 break;
5561 case 4:
5562 ili1 = ad3ili(IL_LD, a2, NME_STR1, MSZ_WORD);
5563 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_ST, ili1, a1, NME_STR1, MSZ_WORD);
5564 break;
5565 case 2:
5566 ili1 = ad3ili(IL_LD, a2, NME_STR1, MSZ_UHWORD);
5567 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_ST, ili1, a1, NME_STR1, MSZ_UHWORD);
5568 break;
5569 default:
5570 ili1 = ad3ili(IL_LD, a2, NME_STR1, MSZ_BYTE);
5571 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_ST, ili1, a1, NME_STR1, MSZ_BYTE);
5572 break;
5573 }
5574 len -= nb;
5575 if (len <= 0)
5576 break;
5577 off += nb;
5578 }
5579 if (bfill) {
5580 len = bfill;
5581 off = str2->lval;
5582 while (true) {
5583 if (ili1)
5584 chk_block(ili1);
5585 if (len > 7) {
5586 ili1 = ad_kcon(0x20202020, 0x20202020);
5587 nb = 8;
5588 } else if (len > 3) {
5589 ili1 = ad_icon(0x20202020);
5590 nb = 4;
5591 } else if (len > 1) {
5592 ili1 = ad_icon(0x2020);
5593 nb = 2;
5594 } else {
5595 ili1 = ad_icon(0x20);
5596 nb = 1;
5597 }
5598 a1 = ad3ili(IL_AADD, addr1, ad_aconi(off), 0);
5599 switch (nb) {
5600 case 8:
5601 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_STKR, ili1, a1, NME_STR1, MSZ_I8);
5602 break;
5603 case 4:
5604 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_ST, ili1, a1, NME_STR1, MSZ_WORD);
5605 break;
5606 case 2:
5607 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_ST, ili1, a1, NME_STR1, MSZ_UHWORD);
5608 break;
5609 default:
5610 ili1 = ad4ili(IL_ST, ili1, a1, NME_STR1, MSZ_BYTE);
5611 break;
5612 }
5613 len -= nb;
5614 if (len <= 0)
5615 break;
5616 off += nb;
5617 }
5618 }
5619 return ili1;
5620}

5622/** \brief Determine if it's possible that the lhs & rhs of a string/character
5623 * assignment can overlap.
5624 *
5625 * Note that for now, an assumed-size char lhs is not a candidate since its
5626 * STRDESC is not marked 'asivar'.
5627 */
5628static bool
5629strovlp(STRDESC *lhs, STRDESC *rhs)
5630{
5631 int rsym;
5632 int lsym;
5633
5634 if (rhs->next != NULL) /* single rhs only */
5635 return true;
5636 if (!rhs->aisvar) /* rhs must be simple var or constant */
5637 return true;
5638 rsym = CONVAL1G(rhs->aval);
5639 if (rsym == 0)
5640 return true;
5641 if (STYPEG(rsym) == ST_CONST)
5642 /* constants never overlaps */
5643 return false;
5644 if (!lhs->aisvar) /* lhs must be simple var */
5645 return true;
5646 lsym = CONVAL1G(lhs->aval);
5647 if (lsym == 0)
5648 return true;
5649 if (lsym != rsym) /* lhs & rhs variables must be different */
5650 return false;
5651 return true;
5652}
5653
5654static char *
5655getcharconst(STRDESC *str)
5656{
5657 int asym;
5658 int sym;
5659 char *p;
5660
5661 if (!str->aisvar || !str->liscon)
5662 return NULL;
5663 asym = str->aval;
5664 sym = CONVAL1G(asym);
5665 if (sym == 0 || STYPEG(sym) != ST_CONST)
5666 return NULL;
5667 p = stb.n_base + (CONVAL1G(sym) + CONVAL2G(asym));
5668 return p;
5669}
5670
5671/*
5672 * fortran compare of strings a1 & a2; returns:
5673 * 0 => strings are the same
5674 * -1 => a1 lexically less than a2
5675 * 1 => a1 lexically greater than a2
5676 * If the lengths of the strings are not equal, the short string is blank
5677 * padded.
5678 */
5679static int
5680_fstrcmp(char *a1, char *a2, int len)
5681{
5682 while (len > 0) {
5683 if (*a1 != *a2) {
5684 if (*a1 > *a2)
5685 return 1;
5686 return -1;
5687 }
5688 ++a1;
5689 ++a2;
5690 --len;
5691 }
5692 return 0;
5693}
5694
5695static int
5696ftn_strcmp(char *a1, char *a2, int a1_len, int a2_len)
5697{
5698 int retv;
5699
5700 if (a1_len == a2_len)
5701 return _fstrcmp(a1, a2, a1_len);
5702
5703 if (a1_len > a2_len) {
5704 /* first compare the first a2_len characters of the strings */
5705 retv = _fstrcmp(a1, a2, a2_len);
5706 if (retv)
5707 return retv;
5708 a1 += a2_len;
5709 a1_len -= a2_len;
5710 /*
5711 * if the last (a1_len - a2_len) characters of a1 are blank, then the
5712 * strings are equal; otherwise, compare the first non-blank char. to
5713 * blank
5714 */
5715 while (a1_len > 0) {
5716 if (*a1 != ' ') {
5717 if (*a1 > ' ')
5718 return 1;
5719 return -1;
5720 }
5721 ++a1;
5722 --a1_len;
5723 }
5724 } else {
5725 /* a2_len > a1_len */
5726 /* first compare the first a1_len characters of the strings */
5727 retv = _fstrcmp(a1, a2, a1_len);
5728 if (retv)
5729 return retv;
5730 a2 += a1_len;
5731 a2_len -= a1_len;
5732 /*
5733 * if the last (a2_len - a1_len) characters of a2 are blank, then the
5734 * strings are equal; otherwise, compare the first non-blank char. to
5735 * blank
5736 */
5737 while (a2_len > 0) {
5738 if (*a2 != ' ') {
5739 if (' ' > *a2)
5740 return 1;
5741 return -1;
5742 }
5743 ++a2;
5744 --a2_len;
5745 }
5746 }
5747 return 0;
5748}

5771static SPTR
5772allochartmp(int lenili)

5780 str_malloc_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_str_malloc_klen);
5781 } else {
5782 str_malloc_nm = mkRteRtnNm(RTE_str_malloc);
5783 }

5785 if (allocharhdr == 0) {

5801 sptr1 = frte_func(mkfunc, str_malloc_nm);

5808 ili = ad2ili(IL_DFRAR, ili, AR(0));
5809 ili = ad3ili(IL_STA, ili, ad_acon(sym, 0), addnme(NT_VAR, sym, 0, 0));
5810 end_ainfo(&ainfo);

5813
5814 DTYPEP(sym, DT_ADDR);

5816}

5818static STRDESC *
5819getstr(int ilm)
5820{
5821 ILM *ilmp;
5822 int addrili, lenili, opc;
5823 STRDESC *list1, *list2, *item;
5824
5825 /* get string descriptor for string ILM */
5826 ilmp = (ILM *)(ilmb.ilm_base + ilm);
5827 if (ILM_OPC(ilmp) == IM_SCAT || ILM_OPC(ilmp) == IM_NSCAT) {
5828 list1 = getstr(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 1));
5829 list2 = getstr(ILM_OPND(ilmp, 2));
5830 item = list1;
5831 list1->cnt += list2->cnt;
5832 while (list1->next)
5833 list1 = list1->next;
5834 list1->next = list2;
5835 if (ILM_OPC(ilmp) == IM_NSCAT)
5836 item->dtype = TY_NCHAR;
5837 } else {
5838 item = (STRDESC *)getitem(STR_AREA, sizeof(STRDESC));
5839 addrili = ILM_RESULT(ilm);
5840 lenili = ILM_CLEN(ilm);
5841 if (IL_TYPE(ILI_OPC(addrili)) == ILTY_CONS &&
5842 SCG(CONVAL1G(ILI_OPND(addrili, 1))) != SC_DUMMY) {
5843 item->aisvar = true;
5844 item->aval = ILI_OPND(addrili, 1);
5845 } else {
5846 item->aisvar = false;
5847 item->aval = addrili;
5848 }
5849 if (IL_TYPE(ILI_OPC(lenili)) == ILTY_CONS) {
5850 item->liscon = true;
5851 item->lval = CONVAL2G(ILI_OPND(lenili, 1));
5852 } else {
5853 item->liscon = false;
5854 item->lval = lenili;
5855 }
5856 item->next = 0;
5857 item->cnt = 1;
5858 item->dtype = TY_CHAR;
5859 opc = ILM_OPC(ilmp);
5860 if (opc == IM_NCHAR || opc == IM_NSUBS || opc == IM_NCHFUNC ||
5861 opc == IM_NSPSEUDOST)
5862 item->dtype = TY_NCHAR;
5863 else if ((ilm = getrval(ilm))) { /* returns sptr or 0 */
5864 DTYPE dtype = DTYPEG(ilm);
5865 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_ARRAY)
5866 dtype = DTySeqTyElement(dtype);
5867 if (DTY(dtype) == TY_NCHAR)
5868 item->dtype = TY_NCHAR;
5869 }
5870 }
5871
5872 return item;
5873}

5893static STRDESC *
5894storechartmp(STRDESC *str, int mxlenili, int clenili)
5895{
5896 INT val[2];
5897 STRDESC *item;
5898 int ilix;
5899 int msz;
5900 int lenili;
5901
5902 msz = MSZ_BYTE;
5903 if (mxlenili)
5904 lenili = mxlenili;
5905 else
5906 lenili = clenili;
5907 if (str->dtype == TY_NCHAR) {
5908 ilix = ad_icon(2L);

5910 msz = MSZ_UHWORD;

5929 item->liscon = false;

5939 chk_block(ilix);
5940 return (item);

5944 chk_block(exp_strcpy(item, str));
5945 return (item);
5946}

5948/**
5949 * \brief return ili for character length of passed length dummy.
5950 */
5951int
5952charlen(SPTR sym)
5953{
5954 SPTR lensym;
5955 int addr;
5956
5957 lensym = CLENG(sym);
5958 if (!INTERNREFG(lensym) && gbl.internal > 1 && INTERNREFG(sym)) {
5959 /* Its len is passed by value in aux.curr_entry->display after sym */
5960 addr = mk_charlen_address(sym);
5961 } else if (PARREFG(lensym) && PASSBYVALG(lensym) && gbl.outlined) {
5962 addr = mk_charlen_parref_sptr(sym);
5963 } else
5964 {
5965 addr = mk_address(lensym);
5966 }
5967 if (DTYPEG(lensym) == DT_INT8)
5968 return ad3ili(IL_LDKR, addr, addnme(NT_VAR, lensym, 0, 0), MSZ_I8);
5969 return ad3ili(IL_LD, addr, addnme(NT_VAR, lensym, 0, 0), MSZ_WORD);
5970}

5982 asym = mk_argasym(sym);

5995/**
5996 \param entbih bih of the entry block
5997 \param exitbih bih of the exit block
5998
5999 Check if this function is a terminal routine (one that does not call any
6000 other routines). If so, the necessary changes will be made to the entry and
6001 exit blocks. This optimization depends on the target machine and its
6002 execution environment. It is appropriate when the target does not have
6003 instructions to manipulate the stack; multiple instructions have to be
6004 generated to allocate stack space, manipulate the frame and stack pointers,
6005 and to check for overflow and underflow.
6006
6007 When the terminal function optimization is appropriate, the following
6008 applies:
6009
6010 1. exceptions and global registers are not used:
6011 a. if the routine is terminal, static space is used in lieu of the
6012 stack. ILIs QENTRY and QEXIT are used.
6013 b. otherwise, faster entry and exit routines, c_i_qentry and
6014 c_i_qexit, are used. The ENTRY ili is modified to locate
6015 c_i_qentry, and a new EXIT ili locating c_i_qexit is generated.
6016 2. otherwise, the ENTRY and EXIT ILIs are left as is.
6017
6018 When the terminal function optimization is not appropriate, the following
6019 applies:
6020
6021 1. if exceptions and global registers are not used, the faster entry and
6022 exit routines, c_i_qentry and c_i_qexit, are used. The ILIs QENTRY and
6023 QEXIT are used.
6024 2. otherwise, the ENTRY and EXIT ILIs are left as is.
6025
6026 The -q 0 256 switch forces full entry and exit to be used.
6027 The -q 0 4096 switch forces QENTRY and QEXIT to be used for all
6028 routines.
6029 */
6030void
6031chk_terminal_func(int entbih, int exitbih)
6032{
6033 aux.curr_entry->auto_array = 0;
6034}

6076#endif

6078void
6079AssignAddresses(void)
6080{
6081 int opc;
6082 reset_global_ilm_position();
6083 do {
6084 int ilmx, len;
6085 int numilms = rdilms();
6086 if (numilms == 0)
6087 break;
6088 for (ilmx = 0; ilmx < numilms; ilmx += len) {
6089 int flen, opnd;
6090 opc = ILM_OPC(ilmx);
6091 flen = len = ilms[opc].oprs + 1;
6092 if (IM_VAR(opc)) {
6093 len += ILM_OPND(ilmx, 1);
6094 }
6095 /* is this a variable reference */
6096 for (opnd = 1; opnd <= flen; ++opnd) {
6097 if (IM_OPRFLAG(opc, opnd) == OPR_SYM) {
6098 SPTR sptr = ILM_SymOPND(ilmx, opnd);
6099 if (sptr > SPTR_NULL && sptr < stb.stg_avail) {
6100 switch (STYPEG(sptr)) {
6101 case ST_CONST:
6102 sym_is_refd(sptr);
6103 break;
6104 case ST_VAR:
6105 case ST_ARRAY:
6106 case ST_STRUCT:
6107 case ST_UNION:
6108 switch (SCG(sptr)) {
6109 case SC_AUTO:
6110 if (!CCSYMG(sptr) && (DINITG(sptr) || SAVEG(sptr))) {
6111 SCP(sptr, SC_STATIC);
6112 sym_is_refd(sptr);
6113 }
6114 break;
6115 case SC_STATIC:
6116 if (!CCSYMG(sptr)) {
6117 sym_is_refd(sptr);
6118 }
6119 break;
6120 default:
6121 break;
6122 }
6123 break;
6124 default:
6125 break;
6126 }
6127 }
6128 }
6129 }
6130 }
6131 } while (opc != IM_END && opc != IM_ENDF);
6132 reset_global_ilm_position();
6133}
